      • buildAccount

        public SipProfile buildAccount(SipProfile account)
        Basic implementation of the account building based on simple implementation fields. A specification of this class could extend and add its own post processing here. Build the account based on preference view contents.
        参数:
        account - The sip profile already saved in database
        返回:
        the sip profile to save into databse based on fields contents.

      • needRestart

        public boolean needRestart()
        Does the wizard changes something that requires to restart sip stack? If so once saved, the wizard will also ask for a stack restart to take into account any preference changed with WizardIface.setDefaultParams(PreferencesWrapper)
        指定者:
        needRestart 在接口中 WizardIface
        覆盖:
        needRestart 在类中 BaseImplementation
        返回:
        true if the wizard would like the sip stack to restart
